Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This move...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He made moves like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:22.37,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:25.92,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find Sai anywhere I looked...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.51,Thinking,,0,0,0,,and he was here all along...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:42.10,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The only way I could see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:44.39,Thinking,,0,0,0,,was by playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.45,0:02:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to play...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,dozens of games, hundreds of games,\Nthousands of games from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,With Isumi-san, with Waya,\Nwith Ochi, with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:03.83,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(340,115)}The Seventy-First Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:03.83,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx330\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}First Comeback Match
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:09.89,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to your match?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go from now on, I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving. Arrange it with the school, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:39.41,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs16\1c&H54625F&\bord0\shad0\frz345\fscy120\move(426,495,352,210)}Japanese Go Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're 3-dan if you win today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your opponent today that guy who\Nhasn't gone to any of his matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, I get an easy promotion through a forfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to get promoted through a win, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou... he came!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that Shindou. Why did he\Nhave to start coming today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Tsujioka-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm playing him for my next Ooteai match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy. I've wanted to play him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You've wanted to play him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a rumor that Touya-kun\Nthinks of him as a rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya-kun!? and Shindou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.08,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:33.66,Background,,0,0,0,,Touya-kun's in the Honinbou league!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:44.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:06:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:03.07,Background,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:27.70,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I played him in the Wakajishisen last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:31.37,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He scared me with a few good moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:36.06,Thinking,,0,0,0,,but he was bad at Yose, and I\Nwon by six and a half moku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:43.77,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But Touya persistently asked me how he played.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:51.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I was annoyed back then because he kept asking about the guy who lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:56.41,Thinking,,0,0,0,,but I guess Touya really did think of him as a rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:02.42,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll play a thick game, and make it hard\Nfor either of us to get territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:10.88,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll bring it into Yose, and defeat him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:14.47,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll show you exactly how bad you are at Yose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:30.53,Background,,0,0,0,,Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:34.16,Background,,0,0,0,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Kaneko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:46.09,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H241917&\fs31\t(0,3987,1,\fs23)\bord0\shad0\fscx100\fscy45\frz346\move(240,214,196,179,0,3987)}Chemistry Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:46.09,Background,,0,0,0,,Kaneko-san, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru was absent today for a match?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. And I hear that he's been absent the last few\Ndays for Go-related things like study sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru cheered up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad for Shindou-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still on short days since\Nsummer break just ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so our homeroom teacher, Mr. Suzuki,\Nwas happy about Shindou cheering up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,despite the fact that he's missing school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He was thinking about quitting as a pro,\Nand now he's ditching school to play Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What a selfish guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just as selfish as he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You suddenly declared that you\Nwere going to the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And before that you only came\Nto the club occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Shindou went back to being a pro\Nbecause he didn't want to study for exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it sound as if you're studying\Nfor exams or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But thanks to Mitani-kun we were able\Nto go to the tournament. It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys made it all the way to the finals...\Nthough all of you lost to Kaiou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You girls won your first 3-0, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah we did. Wasn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you 3rd year students\Nare leaving the Go club...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do all by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Koike-kun, a senpai of ours called Tsutsui-san\Nstarted this Go club all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,By himself!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:28.73,Background,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:34.66,Background,,0,0,0,,Tsutsui-san started it by himself, then Hikaru\Njoined in, and I tagged along with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:41.12,Background,,0,0,0,,Then Hikaru dragged Mitani-kun\Nin. That's how it started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:45.37,Background,,0,0,0,,After that, Kaneko-san came temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:47.79,Background,,0,0,0,,And Natsume-kun and Kumiko-san joined.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how the Haze Jr. High Go club was formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun having lots of people, but it's\Nalso fun starting up by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your Go club from now on, Koike-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mine!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My Go club...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat Kaiou someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:20.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The Haze Jr. High Go club is changing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:22.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Everyone's changing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:27.54,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Even Hikaru, who was about to quit being\Na pro, has started playing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:33.92,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Hikaru... I'm sure he's sitting in front of\Na Go board with a stern face right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, I'm so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I got lucky there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I have to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:01.99,Background,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That game right now, it looked like one\Nof our games, you were doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Isumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You went to Shindou's place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How was Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't quite understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But... it seems like he's over it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We both got to play a good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard, making us worry like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:16.40,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can't just surround territory right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:51.48,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Kids these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.07,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sakamaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Sighing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Amano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Amano-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Ogata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Amano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Do you have some time right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You were asking about Shindou Hikaru first\Ndan earlier weren't you, Master Ogata?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... yes... oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou came to his match...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:18.06,Background,,0,0,0,,Okay... okay... thank you for calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.02,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:34.04,Background,,0,0,0,,Yes... yes... what!? I'll check up on it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the editor-in-chief isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Master Kuwabara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, the manuscript you asked me for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you for bringing it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I had some business in the area, so I brought it by.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Amano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing. I was just thinking about something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kuwabara, you were talking about Shindou\NHikaru first dan the other day weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,About how he will come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I was right, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But why is everyone so\Ninterested in Shindou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kuwabara, Master Ogata, Master\NKurata, even Master Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's what we all want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so impatient. I'm sure we'll\Nall eventually find out, Amano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My sixth sense tells me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixth sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:47.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:49.92,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:20.00,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Why is someone this strong here? How can I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:15.97,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya-kun's done, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:19.10,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What!? He's leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Without watching Shindou-kun's first comeback match?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He'd want to watch it if he was a rival...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:31.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Maybe that rumor's false...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:38.07,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:46.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:50.25,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Maybe he thinks a match against a lower-dan\Nplayer isn't worth watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:59.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Only I can measure Shindou's strength now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:05.89,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I knew it the moment he appeared\Nin front of me that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:15.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, I received the pairings for the first round\Nof the first preliminaries of the Meijin match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:18.66,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya-kun's opponent for the first round was...
