Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would you go, Mai-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:21.58,Background,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you want to play there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.89,0:22:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to increase Black's territory, and\Nget in the way of White's territory.
