Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.27,0:22:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one way of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:33.36,Background,,0,0,0,,Other than this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:37.93,Background,,0,0,0,,You can play here to try to solidify\NBlack's territory here,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.60,0:22:35.80,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(167,0)\3c&H028A08&\4c&H028A08&\fscx100\fscy90\bord1\shad0.5\move(720,367,325,367)}Attempt to solidify Black's territory.
