Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.19,0:22:49.66,Background,,0,0,0,,These are all good moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When you have lots of different paths\Nto take, choose one suited to yourself.
