Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:02.61,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Is the new wave really coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:07.03,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Is Shindou-kun's strength real?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.37,0:23:12.16,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I won't let these young ones take the world just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:26.22,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya... I want to play against you, as soon as possible.
